Nothing at all.

75
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,040
I heard Shan Junhao was hit by a car

76
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:38,160
before he came back.

77
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:41,550
Mr. Zhang,

78
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,760
we’re businessmen

79
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,920
and can only do business.

80
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,640
Perhaps we can use Ye Qianyu

81
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,200
to destroy Shan Junhao.

82
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:56,950
Dig up everything on her.

83
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:57,760
Be quick.

84
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:00,640
Yes.

85
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:13,670
Zhao Qun.

86
00:05:15,670 --> 00:05:17,760
Go to Guanmei Fishing Village tomorrow.

87
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,070
I don’t trust their words.

88
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,040
Yes, boss.

89
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:29,950
Junhao.

90
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,440
This is your favorite.

91
