Eat up. You need more nutrients.

92
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:38,200
You suffered a lot.

93
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,790
Look how skinny and tanned are you!

94
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,510
Aunt Jiang. You should eat more, too.

95
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:45,160
OK.

96
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,230
You, too.

97
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,110
Where was I

98
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,510
over the past few months?

99
00:05:54,230 --> 00:05:55,110
I only remember

100
