101
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:05,230
You were in Guanmei Fishing...

102
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,350
You were there...

103
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:07,950
Yes.

104
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:13,160
