115
00:06:39,790 --> 00:06:40,720
I can’t wait

116
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:44,000
to have Yunyi as my daughter-in-law.

117
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,390
The engagement

118
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:50,670
is simply a formality.

119
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,720
Since I put on this ring,

120
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,070
I’ve already regarded Junhao

121
00:06:59,670 --> 00:07:00,950
as my husband.

122
00:07:07,110 --> 00:07:08,200
This ring...

123
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,880
What’s wrong, Junhao?

124
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,640
Are you OK?

125
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:28,950
I’m fine.

126
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,440
Just a mild headache.

127
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,510
Junhao.

128
00:07:33,350 --> 00:07:35,270
The doctor said you injured your head,

129
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:37,950
so you need to rest well for some time.

130
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:39,880
Don’t force yourself

131
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,200
to recall anything.

132
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,110
Try to relax yourself.

133
00:07:47,790 --> 00:07:48,950
Look,

134
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:51,040
