143
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:27,220
Do you want some?

144
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:28,980
Thanks.

145
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:36,460
Tonghao?

146
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:38,500
Liyin,

147
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:39,980
