158
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,700
Tonghao is Qianyu’s first love.

159
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:09,540
I bet they can’t get their hands

160
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:12,640
off each other.

161
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:14,620
