164
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,260
That is strange.

165
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,820
Jinzhi loves money.

166
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:28,470
She didn’t close the store on typhoon days,

167
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:32,140
