175
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:53,140
It can’t be a coincidence.

176
00:10:55,960 --> 00:11:01,550
Are we right that he really is Shan Junhao?

177
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:05,140
You are.

178
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:09,500
Tonghao is Shan Junhao.

179
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:20,080
You’re back.

180
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,760
- Welcome back. - Welcome.

181
00:11:29,230 --> 00:11:30,020
Qianyu.

182
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,000
Tang said you’d be back today,

183
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:34,020
