189
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:48,880
Thank you.

190
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,020
Thanks. Thanks.

191
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,640
Jinzhi,

192
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,150
don’t you always

193
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,670
