194
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,880
It will soon come true.

195
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:59,060
I heard

196
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:01,860
Shan Junhao is a billionaire.

197
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:03,580
Jinzhi,

198
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:05,710
when you become his mother-in-law,

199
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,280
don’t forget about us.

200
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:08,640
Hey, Qianyu,

201
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:10,470
now that you’re

202
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:11,910
Shan Junhao’s girlfriend,

203
00:12:12,350 --> 00:12:13,580
the debt

204
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:14,980
we owe Senwell

205
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,110
can be written off, right?

206
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:17,150
Of course.

207
00:12:17,350 --> 00:12:19,280
That’s only a drop in the bucket

208
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,320
