209
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:23,710
Consider it a betrothal present.

210
00:12:23,710 --> 00:12:24,670
Yeah.

211
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:25,230
Right. Right.

212
00:12:26,110 --> 00:12:26,710
Hey, guys,

213
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:27,710
that’s enough.

214
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,280
Money and love

215
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,590
can’t be mixed together.

216
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,960
They’re irrelevant.

217
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,710
Fine. Alright.

218
00:12:35,470 --> 00:12:37,110
Let’s eat the cake.

219
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,180
Yes.

220
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:39,820
- Yes. Let’s eat. - Yes. Let’s eat.

221
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:42,910
Qianyu.

222
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:45,000
What happened?

223
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,790
What’s wrong?

224
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:48,470
What’s up?

225
00:12:48,470 --> 00:12:50,080
Tonghao or Shan Junhao

226
00:12:50,590 --> 00:12:52,080
