230
00:13:02,110 --> 00:13:02,910
Yeah.

231
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,030
There, there.

232
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:18,640
Don’t cry.

233
00:13:20,470 --> 00:13:21,960
