234
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:29,910
Mom,

235
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:33,400
I’m heartbroken.

236
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,440
I know.

237
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:40,660
I understand.

238
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:45,220
But that’s what love is.

239
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:48,060
It can bring you joys

240
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:50,980
as well as sorrows.

241
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:56,790
What should I do?

242
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,520
What about my life?

243
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:02,740
Failed relationships can help you grow.

244
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:05,820
You should learn to accept it

245
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:07,880
and let it go.

246
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,620
In the end,

247
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,350
we can only rely on ourselves.

248
00:14:15,590 --> 00:14:18,140
Even if everyone abandons you,

249
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:21,860
you should live well on your own.

250
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:28,340
You have to be responsible for your own life.

251
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:32,620
When exactly

252
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:34,460
will the pain stop?

253
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:37,980
Time isn’t a cure.

254
00:14:38,470 --> 00:14:39,900
It can’t heal you

255
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:44,300
but can numb your heart.

256
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:50,380
You’ll be fine

257
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,700
in a while.

258
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:18,520
It’s a new day to make money.

259
00:15:19,230 --> 00:15:22,150
Go, go, go!

260
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:29,670
Welcome.

261
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,420
What are you doing here?

262
00:15:42,780 --> 00:15:44,420
I’d like to talk to Ye Qianyu.

263
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:48,820
She has nothing to say to you.

264
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:09,500
= One Million RMB =

265
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:10,980
What do you mean?

266
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:14,780
I know you need money,

267
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,260
so I’m here to make you an offer.

268
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:19,300
What is it?

269
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:20,820
First,

270
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:22,900
don’t tell others

271
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:24,780
about the past between you and Junhao.

272
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:26,700
Second,

273
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:29,820
don’t ever show up in front of him again.

274
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,860
Tonghao is worth this much, huh?

275
00:16:40,910 --> 00:16:41,910
Will you take it or not?

276
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:48,060
Did Tonghao ask you to come here?

277
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:50,340
You made up

278
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,660
that name.

279
00:16:54,470 --> 00:16:55,670
You used his amnesia

280
00:16:55,710 --> 00:16:57,200
to manipulate him.

281
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,670
That’s not love

282
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:00,520
but pure deception.

283
00:17:01,350 --> 00:17:02,100
Luckily,

284
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:04,230
he’s got his memory back

285
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:06,350
and won’t fall for your lie again.

286
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,040
I never deceived him.

287
00:17:08,710 --> 00:17:10,280
What he experienced in Guanmei

288
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:11,380
is real.

289
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:14,110
Junhao is the GM of Senwell,

290
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,880
yet you hid him on purpose

291
00:17:16,950 --> 00:17:18,400
and kept his whereabouts secret.

