583
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,230
A trip for two is different from traveling alone.

584
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,310
Go away.

585
00:33:28,350 --> 00:33:29,880
I’ve been alone on the way for too long.

586
00:33:30,590 --> 00:33:32,350
What will it be like

587
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:36,040
if I have company?

588
00:34:01,830 --> 00:34:04,000
I love you, Qianyu.

589
00:34:26,390 --> 00:34:27,870
Mama Jinzhi.

590
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:29,390
Shengzhe.

591
00:34:29,910 --> 00:34:31,320
Where are you?

592
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,630
Open the door for me.

593
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:38,910
Good morning.

594
00:35:40,630 --> 00:35:41,520
Why are you here?

595
00:35:44,120 --> 00:35:44,800
You forgot

596
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:46,190
I told you story last night?

597
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:47,710
You dozed off before I finished.

598
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:48,800
When I meant to go back,

599
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,840
I found Mama Jinzhi had locked the door.

600
00:35:57,910 --> 00:35:59,950
Did you sleep well?

601
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:01,910
Did I disturb you?

602
00:36:03,470 --> 00:36:04,080
What do you think?

603
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:06,000
It’s Chen’s fault.

604
00:36:06,430 --> 00:36:07,950
How dare she lock the door!

605
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,710
Mama Jinzhi is adorable.

606
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:13,000
Adorable?

607
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,080
You can have her then.

608
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:17,760
After years of her torture,

609
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,870
it’s a miracle

610
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,430
that I grow up alive.

611
00:36:21,390 --> 00:36:22,460
Qianyu,

612
00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:24,470
I do envy you sometimes.

613
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:26,430
For what?

614
00:36:27,040 --> 00:36:28,760
Your mom is fun,

615
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:30,760
and your younger brother is cute.

616
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,420
Growing up in this kind of family

617
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:33,380
is a delight.

618
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:34,220
Fun?

619
00:36:35,140 --> 00:36:36,320
Cute?

620
00:36:40,620 --> 00:36:41,800
I’m delighted

621
00:36:42,910 --> 00:36:43,870
but we’re still poor.

622
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:46,150
I envy you, too.

623
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,910
You can tour around the world

624
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:50,150
and live a carefree life.

625
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:51,190
Unlike me,

626
00:36:51,430 --> 00:36:52,600
if I want to head to downtown,

627
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:55,040
I’ll have to check if I have enough gas money.

628
00:36:56,710 --> 00:36:57,760
What’s there to envy?

629
00:36:58,390 --> 00:36:59,870
It’s true that I’ve been to a lot of places,

630
00:37:00,190 --> 00:37:02,320
but I do also feel tired and lonely sometimes

631
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:04,800
and want to settle down

632
00:37:04,950 --> 00:37:07,430
to live a peaceful life.

633
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:10,120
Guanmei is a perfect choice.

634
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:11,470
You want to stay here?

635
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:13,560
You don’t welcome me?

636
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:14,670
No, no.

637
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,430
I didn’t mean that.

638
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:18,230
Then what’s your concern?

639
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:20,470
Nothing.

640
00:37:23,470 --> 00:37:24,320
But...

641
00:37:24,470 --> 00:37:26,190
Why Guanmei?

642
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,520
Because of you.

643
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:38,470
I was joking.

644
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,430
Don’t take it seriously.

645
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:43,840
You aren’t my type,

646
00:37:45,190 --> 00:37:46,040
lion.

647
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:53,360
What are you doing here? Go away!

648
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:03,320
Qianyu. Taichu.

649
00:38:03,840 --> 00:38:05,230
Are you up?

650
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:07,800
Breakfast is ready.

651
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:14,190
I’m so embarrassed because of you.

652
00:38:19,950 --> 00:38:20,910
Morning, Mama Jinzhi.

653
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:22,520
Morning, Taichu.

654
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:24,320
Did you sleep well?

655
00:38:25,430 --> 00:38:26,670
Not too bad.

656
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,670
Good. Great.

657
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:31,390
Come down for breakfast.

658
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:32,870
I’m not hungry.

659
00:38:32,910 --> 00:38:33,710
I’m needed elsewhere.

660
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,520
Gotta go.

661
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:36,560
OK.

662
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,520
What are you looking at?

663
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:05,390
Forget about it.

664
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:07,190
You should get rid of

665
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:09,150
that guy’s stuff.

666
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,360
Will that help her forget about him?

667
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:15,120
What Qianyu needs is time.

668
00:39:16,950 --> 00:39:19,390
But keeping it is of no help at all.

669
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:25,670
I wish you could lose your memory.

670
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,190
Qianyu.

671
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:38,080
Believe me.

672
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:40,230
Everything will be fine.

673
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:44,800
You should distract yourself.

674
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:50,470
Taichu is nice to you.

675
00:39:52,710 --> 00:39:53,390
Chen Jinzhi.

676
00:39:53,670 --> 00:39:55,600
Qianyu’s mind is already a mess.

677
00:39:55,910 --> 00:39:57,600
Don’t make it bigger.

678
00:39:57,950 --> 00:39:59,190
What did I do wrong?

679
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:05,020
Mom,

680
00:40:05,470 --> 00:40:06,670
I can’t use Taichu.

681
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:08,470
Don’t push him to me.

682
00:40:12,910 --> 00:40:13,430
Yes.

683
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,320
Hey,

684
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:16,800
you should leave her alone.

685
00:40:19,670 --> 00:40:21,670
When I see that Shan Junhao again,

686
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,630
I’ll chop him into pieces.

687
00:40:33,120 --> 00:40:33,940
Junhao.

688
00:40:34,870 --> 00:40:36,220
I made you coffee.

689
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:38,950
Thank you.

690
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:48,220
Junhao.

691
00:40:49,120 --> 00:40:51,000
The doctor said you haven’t fully recovered.

692
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,120
Don’t exhaust yourself.

693
00:40:52,470 --> 00:40:53,040
I’m fine.

694
00:40:54,390 --> 00:40:56,040
The board meeting is tomorrow.

695
00:40:56,950 --> 00:40:58,430
I need to familiarize myself

696
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:00,120
with the progress of all projects

697
00:41:00,870 --> 00:41:02,710
launched during my absence,

698
00:41:04,190 --> 00:41:05,320
to regain control

699
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,600
of the company.

700
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,430
What’s wrong?

701
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:15,430
Nothing.

702
00:41:17,230 --> 00:41:18,600
I’m content seeing you like this.

703
00:41:29,870 --> 00:41:31,000
Thanks for coming.

704
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:31,840
Please.

705
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,430
- Let’s go. - Thanks.

706
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:35,320
Qianyu.

707
00:41:38,120 --> 00:41:39,390
Su Liyin.

708
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:41,230
What do you have for me?

709
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:42,870
Ye Qianyu.

710
00:41:43,120 --> 00:41:45,430
Why was your letter delivered to our inn?

711
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:48,120
My letter?

712
00:41:54,910 --> 00:41:56,040
Qianyu.

713
00:41:56,120 --> 00:41:58,150
I hope you can come to Senwell tomorrow.

714
00:41:58,230 --> 00:41:59,320
I need you.

715
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:01,080
Shan Junhao.

716
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:04,120
Why did Tonghao ask you to go to Senwell?

717
00:42:04,390 --> 00:42:05,080
Qianyu.

718
00:42:05,320 --> 00:42:06,670
Tonghao wrote you a letter?

719
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:08,430
He sent his assistant

720
00:42:08,430 --> 00:42:09,520
to come and see us yesterday.

721
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:12,840
Ye Qianyu. You’re such a lucky gal!

722
00:42:13,190 --> 00:42:15,120
The guy you found turned out to be a billionaire.

723
00:42:15,950 --> 00:42:18,600
It seems your dream will soon come true.

724
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:30,100
What’s wrong with Qianyu?

725
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:32,840
Qianyu. Let’s go out to have fun.

726
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,470
Do you want me to teach that jerk a lesson?

727
00:42:37,620 --> 00:42:39,000
Let’s go see dolphins.

728
00:42:45,140 --> 00:42:46,120
Taichu.

729
00:42:46,670 --> 00:42:48,000
Thank you for trying to comfort me,

730
00:42:49,140 --> 00:42:49,940
but...

731
00:42:50,390 --> 00:42:51,560
I’m not in the mood.

732
00:42:52,470 --> 00:42:53,470
I’m going back.

733
00:43:04,630 --> 00:43:07,150
Shan Junhao wrote a letter to Qianyu?

734
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:07,950
Sheng,

735
00:43:08,190 --> 00:43:09,390
you just said

736
00:43:09,710 --> 00:43:11,360
his assistant was here.

737
00:43:11,760 --> 00:43:12,390
Yes.

738
00:43:12,670 --> 00:43:13,910
What did he say?

739
00:43:15,190 --> 00:43:17,080
He asked about

740
00:43:17,120 --> 00:43:18,430
what Tonghao did here.

741
00:43:18,470 --> 00:43:19,950
Nothing special.

742
00:43:21,390 --> 00:43:23,430
His assistant didn’t know anything.

743
00:43:23,950 --> 00:43:25,390
He didn’t know the name Tonghao,

744
00:43:25,390 --> 00:43:26,360
or why he ended up here.

745
00:43:26,470 --> 00:43:27,910
He knew nothing.

746
00:43:28,950 --> 00:43:30,040
I see. Thank you.

747
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:32,040
You’re welcome.

748
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:54,480
♪ Distance between us ♪

749
00:43:57,760 --> 00:44:02,800
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

750
00:44:04,040 --> 00:44:08,520
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

751
00:44:08,520 --> 00:44:11,680
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

752
00:44:12,240 --> 00:44:19,520
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

753
00:44:20,840 --> 00:44:25,120
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

754
00:44:25,120 --> 00:44:28,880
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

755
00:44:29,120 --> 00:44:33,400
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

756
00:44:33,400 --> 00:44:36,800
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

757
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:41,640
♪ You painted my life ♪

758
00:44:41,640 --> 00:44:45,200
♪ With flowers ♪

759
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:49,160
♪ You raised me up ♪

760
00:44:49,160 --> 00:44:52,320
♪ From that moment on ♪

761
00:44:53,080 --> 00:44:56,040
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪
